# IAP Pet Download Files

Place downloaded `.catpet` files in this directory for deployment.

These files are copied into the built site during deployment (see `deploy.sh`) so users can download premium pets via the website.

## Directory Structure

```
pets/
├── .gitkeep
├── ragdoll/
│   └── pet.catpet
├── british/
│   └── pet.catpet
├── shiba/
│   └── pet.catpet
├── corgi/
│   └── pet.catpet
└── husky/
    └── pet.catpet
```

## Usage

1. Download IAP pet `.catpet` files from the macOS App Store build
2. Place them in the corresponding subdirectory
3. Run `pnpm docs:build` and deploy
4. The deploy script will automatically copy the `pets/` folder to the built site
